author: Dragon_Master_48
title: A decent spinner...
review:
This spinner, although not the best, provides many good pieces/weapons for other spinners, and also goes well on its own.

Pros

  • Zane DX.
  • Red and Golden/White Spinner.
  • Spear works really well.

 

Cons

  • Flail and katana are sort of... simple.

 

This spinner is decent and holds up against other spinners. If you are looking to add to your collection, this spinner would be a good addition.

author: Blazing_Brick
title: The Best Fighter of the Spinners!
review: This set includes Zane DX,a great figure,and many other excellent elements.His Golden Flail is great;I have lost less than 5 matches with it,and I've played with it at least 300 times.His cards were great,and this set even included Chain Crazy.His other weapons include a spear[a new kind] and a black katana.His spinner design is the Ice Emblem displayed on ice with more ice floating around.His spinner is red on the bottom and gold on top.He is great overall;I highly recommend him.

author: digi_raptor
title: Good spinner
review:
Great spinner with good cards, spinner and minifigure.

The only thing that I would like to be better, is the accessories as I would've liked to see a weapon that would fit Zane more e.g. a weapon with shurikens as the golden weapon looks more like a Jay weapon than anything else, Cole got a scythe, so why can't Zane get a shuriken related weapon? Parts only get a 3 as it's a spinner set

 

Overall good spinner set
